  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/25/89228e54199230aba113f6bbb00f5999.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/27/648dbc568dc2ee5bc50546f492d6be23.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 45px; width: 45px; float: left;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">其实商务信函对于写作者的基本要求不外乎几点，语法准确、陈述事实、编排合理。在撰写商务信函之时，由于细节颇多，不知道该如何抒发，那么应该如何逻辑清晰地安排信函内容？</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Shirley Taylor在她的书（《Model Business Letters, Emails & Other Business Document》）中提出了基本的</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">四点方案</strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">：</span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/27/1b00f6f481ff3ea559f313970dd17f45.png\" /></div>\n<div>\n\t这个四点方案有助于我们在撰写时保持清晰的头脑，不漏掉重要的信息，同时也可以保证一定的逻辑。在进行BEC考试时，也可以使用这种方法，将要求表达的内容排个顺序，然后不慌不忙地完成~</div>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t<strong>1. O</strong><strong>pening or introduction </strong><strong>开头或简述</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t第一段陈述写信的原因，基本明确信件内容。可包括以下内容：<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">告知收到来信/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">提及一次见面或接触/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">引出要谈论的事情</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #0066ff;\"><span style=\"color: #faebd7;\"><strong>Examples</strong></span></span></p>\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 600px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tThank you for your letter of&hellip;</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tIt was good to meet you again at last week&rsquo;s conference.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tWe wish to hold out annual conference at a London hotel in September.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2. C</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">entral section (details) </strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">主体部分（细节）</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t每部分内容独立成段，细节陈述简单清楚。最终应导向一个符合逻辑、自然而然的结论。</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t<strong>3. </strong><strong>Conclusion (action or response) </strong><strong>结论（行动或回应）</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t这部分应得出符合逻辑的结论：<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">表明希望收信人采取何种行动/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">说明鉴于上述情况你将采取什么行动</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 102, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 235, 215);\"><strong>Examples</strong></span></span></p>\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; width: 600px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tPlease let me have full details of the costs involved, together with some sample menus.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tIf payment is not received within seven days, this matter will be placed in the hands of our solicitor.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t<strong>4.&nbsp;</strong><strong>Close </strong><strong>结尾</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18.0pt;\">\n\t通常只需要简单一行字，与信件内容呼应。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 102, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 235, 215);\"><strong>Examples</strong></span></span></p>\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; width: 600px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tI look forward to meeting you soon.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tI look forward to seeing you at next month&rsquo;s conference.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 40px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\tI would appreciate your prompt reply.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Please call me if you have any question.</span></div>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; margin-left: 18pt;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 80px;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/27/a940ece94b2d8eda9f4c25061af679bf.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; float: left; height: 46px; width: 45px;\" /><font color=\"#4b0082\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 204, 0);\"><b>然后</b></span></font></div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"color: #4b0082;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffcc00;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">来看一个实例</span></strong></span></span><strong><br />\n\t</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t\n\t<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\t\tINSTITUTE OF SECRETARIES</div>\n\t<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\t\tWilson House, West Street, London SW1 2AR<br />\n\t\tTelephone 020 89872432<br />\n\t\tFax 020 89872556</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tLD/ST(<strong>作者/打字员</strong>)<br />\n\t\t12 May 201-</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tMiss Ong Lee Fong(<strong>信内地址</strong>)<br />\n\t\t15 Windsor Road<br />\n\t\tManchester<br />\n\t\tM2 9GJ</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tDear Lee Fong<strong>(通常考试是从这里开始写)</strong><br />\n\t\t201-SECRETARIES CONFERENCE, 8/9 OCTOBER 201-</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tI have pleasure in inviting you to attend our special conference to be held at the Clifton Hotel, London on Tuesday/Wednsday 8/9 October 201-.<strong>(开头，交代了目的，时间地点)</strong></div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tThis <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/intensive\" target=\"_blank\">intensive</a>, practical conference for professional secretaries aims to:<strong>(细节，举例说明会议的内容，强调会议的益处)</strong><br />\n\t\t&diams;Increase your managerial and office productivity<br />\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">&diams;</span>Improve your communicational skills<br />\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">&diams;</span>Bring you up to date with the latest technology and techniques<br />\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">&diams;</span>Enable <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/networking\" target=\"_blank\">networking</a> with other secretaries</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tThe seminar is power-packed with a distinguished panel of professional speakers who will give expert advice on many useful topics. A programme is enclosed giving full details of this seminar, which I know you will not want to miss.</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tIf you would like to join us, please complete the enclosed registration form and return it to me before 30 June with your fee of &pound;50 per person.<strong>(结论)</strong></div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tI look forward to seeing you again at this exciting conference.<strong>(结尾)</strong></div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tYours sincerely<br />\n\t\t<strong><em>Louise Dunscombe<br />\n\t\t</em></strong>Louise Dunscombe(Mrs)<br />\n\t\tConference Organiser</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\tEncs<strong>(表示有附件)</strong></div>\n\t</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/27/ac2b0bf43f94380beeabf326f4b3f22c.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 44px; width: 45px; float: left;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">对于相关内容有疑问或意见的请留言哦~</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p798241/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p798241\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798512/\">世界身高报告：荷兰人最高 你猜中国人排第几</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797664/\">2万封邮件爆希拉里选举黑幕 川普表示我笑了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798242/\">囧研究：多少钱够你维持一段友谊？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797394/\">套路还是老的好：人家再也不要网络相亲了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p797635/\">视频：老美来教你！地道美语发音要这么练</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p798521/\">5部提高英式英语